{
  "id": "adv_card_rio_06_02",
  "title": "神崎莉央 2話 娘をよろしく！？",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_station-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "station-00-noon",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "sfx",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-out-single-01.m4a",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_06_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_06_02-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "莉央さん、疲れてませんか？　昨日はライブだったし\n新幹線で少しは眠ってくれて良かったのに",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Rio-san‚ aren't you tired? We had a live performance yesterday‚ and\nIt would've been good if you got some sleep on the Shinkansen.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 5.3333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_06_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_06_02-rio001.m4a",
      "text": "け、結構よ……\n昨日は打ち上げの後、ぐっすり眠ったから",
      "translations": {
        "en": "N-no‚ I'm fine…\nbecause I slept soundly after the after-party last night.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 10.8333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_station-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "station-00-noon",
      "startTime": 14.3
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_06_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_06_02-rio002.m4a",
      "text": "……貴方が実家に来るのが気になって\n眠るどころじゃなかったわよ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…I couldn't sleep because I was worried about you\ncoming to my hometown!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 17.0666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_station-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "station-00-noon",
      "startTime": 19.4666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_06_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_06_02-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "ん？　何か言いましたか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Huh? Did you say something?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 19.4666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_station-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "station-00-noon",
      "startTime": 22.0333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_06_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_06_02-rio003.m4a",
      "text": "な、なんでもないわよ！\n独り言を聞かないでちょうだい！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "N-nothing at all!\nPlease don't listen to my mumbling!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 24,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_phone-tap-02.m4a",
          "delay": 6766.666666700001,
          "startTime": 30.7666666667
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_station-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "station-00-noon",
      "startTime": 26.2
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_06_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_06_02-rio004.m4a",
      "text": "はぁ……母に電話を掛けるから\nそこでちょっと待っていてもらえる？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ugh… I'm going to make a call my mother now.\nCan you wait here for a bit?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 30.4333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_station-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "station-00-noon",
      "startTime": 34.8000010173
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_06_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_06_02-rio005.m4a",
      "text": "――もしもし、お母さん？\n今日これからそっちに帰るつもりなんだけど……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "――Hello‚ Mom?\nI'm planning to come over to your place later today…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 36.8666676839,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_station-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "station-00-noon",
      "startTime": 39.8333343506
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_06_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_06_02-rio006.m4a",
      "text": "その……紹介したい人を連れて行ってもいいかしら？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Well‚ there's someone I want to introduce to you. Is that okay?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 39.8333343506,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "莉央の母",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio’s",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "もちろん、大歓迎よ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Of course‚ you're very welcome!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 44.1666676839,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "莉央の母",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio’s",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "楽しいお正月になりそうね。お友達？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It seems like it will be a fun New Year. Is this a friend?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 46.5000010173,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_station-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "station-00-noon",
      "startTime": 50.1000010173
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_06_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_06_02-rio007.m4a",
      "text": "……友達じゃないわ。私のマネージャーよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…He's not a friend. He's my manager.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 50.1000010173,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_station-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "station-00-noon",
      "startTime": 53.8333343506
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "莉央の母",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio’s",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "まあまあ！　莉央が前、話してくれた方ね！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Oh my! You're the gentleman Rio mentioned before‚ right?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 53.8333343506,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "莉央の母",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio’s",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "若いのに、とっても優秀で将来が楽しみな男性だって",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I've heard that you're young‚ but talented with a bright future.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 57.7333343506,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_06_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_06_02-rio008.m4a",
      "text": "そ、そこまでは言ってないわよ\nとにかく、彼が挨拶をしたいって言ってるの",
      "translations": {
        "en": "W-wait a minute! I didn't say all that…\nAnyway‚ he wants to greet you‚",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 65.3000010173,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_station-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "station-00-noon",
      "startTime": 68.7666676839
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_06_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_06_02-rio009.m4a",
      "text": "嫌ならいいの。私がうまく言っておくから――",
      "translations": {
        "en": "and if you don't want to‚ it's fine. I can explain things――",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 68.7666676839,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_station-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "station-00-noon",
      "startTime": 71.6333343506
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "莉央の母",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio’s",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "何を言ってるの。もちろんお会いするわ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "What are you talking about? Of course‚ I'll meet him.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 71.6333343506,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "莉央の母",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio’s",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "日頃、莉央がお世話になっているお礼を言わないと",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I have to express my gratitude for taking care of Rio.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 75.2333343506,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_06_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_06_02-rio010.m4a",
      "text": "……そ、そう",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…R-right.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 78.6000010173,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "莉央の母",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio’s",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "それにしても、莉央がお正月に男性を",
      "translations": {
        "en": "By the way‚ Rio bringing a man home for New Year's…!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 80.6000010173,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "莉央の母",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio’s",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "連れて来るなんて……！　お母さん、嬉しいわ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I'm so glad.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 83.5666676839,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_station-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "station-00-noon",
      "startTime": 87.9666676839
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_06_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_06_02-rio011.m4a",
      "text": "えっ！？　ちょっとお母さん、そういう意味じゃ――",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Sorry? It's not like that――",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 87.9666676839,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "莉央の母",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio’s",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "歓迎の準備をして待ってるわね、それじゃ後で！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I'll get prepared to welcome him. Then See you soon!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 90.5666676839,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_phone-end-03.m4a",
          "delay": 4266.6666667000045,
          "startTime": 94.8333343506
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_station-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "station-00-noon",
      "startTime": 97.4333343506
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_06_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_06_02-rio012.m4a",
      "text": "待って、お母さん！　彼はそんなんじゃ……\n……電話、切れてる",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Wait‚ Mom! He's not like…\n…The call got disconnected.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 98.8666676839,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_station-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "station-00-noon",
      "startTime": 100.8333343506
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_06_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_06_02-rio013.m4a",
      "text": "ああもう！　すっかり誤解されてるわ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ugh! She totally misunderstood!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 100.8333343506,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_06_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_06_02-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "ちょっと莉央さん、相談があるんですが……\nん？　様子が変ですよ？　どうしたんですか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hold on‚ Rio-san. I have something to discuss…\nHuh? Your behavior seems strange. What's wrong?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 107.6000010173,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_station-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "station-00-noon",
      "startTime": 112.0000010173
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_06_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_06_02-rio014.m4a",
      "text": "だから！　なんでもないわよ！\nそれより相談って何よ！！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I told you‚ it's nothing!\nMore importantly‚ what's the discussion you're talking about!!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 113.9666676839,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_station-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "station-00-noon",
      "startTime": 115.9333343506
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_06_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_06_02-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "な、何怒ってるんですか……\n莉央さんのお母さんに買ってきたお土産なんですけど",
      "translations": {
        "en": "W-why are you getting mad…\nI bought a souvenir for your mother‚",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 118.6000010173,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_06_02/sud_vo_adv_card_rio_06_02-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "普通の菓子折だけで良かったんでしょうか？\n俺としては、喜んでもらえるようもっと気合いを……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "but is a regular sweet box okay?\nI thought I should put more effort into it to make her happy…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 125.9000010173,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_station-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "station-00-noon",
      "startTime": 129.5333343506
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
